{"tid":1727640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高志森執導的南海十三郎 因台前幕後集體辭演 最後決定取消","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T14:46:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d623ad16ab0673022e9d1f310de9fa3b281db4be","tid":1727640,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"在facebook群組「文人多說話」今日（16/11）有網民爆料，指出《南海十三郎》一眾台前幕後早前集體辭演，有劇場中人向記者確認消息屬實，惟沒有具體透露他們為何辭演。雖然高志森暫時未就此事回覆記者，但春天實驗劇團卻有發通告指演出延後：「因香港政治環境及治安因素關係，本團決定2020年4月於西九戲曲中心的《南海十三郎》演出延後，特此通告，帶來不便，望大家理解。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/399113/%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E5%8A%87-%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E9%83%8E-2020%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%94%E5%BB%B6%E5%BE%8C-%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%B0%E5%89%8D%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%BE%AD%E6%BC%94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F399113%2F%25E8%2588%259E%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%258A%2587-%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%258D%2581%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%2583%258E-2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E5%25BE%258C-%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%259B%25A0%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%259B%2586%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%25BE%25AD%25E6%25BC%2594&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=76b60af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/399113/%E8%88%9E%E5%8F%B0%E5%8A%87-%E5%8D%97%E6%B5%B7%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E9%83%8E-2020%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8D%E6%BC%94%E5%BB%B6%E5%BE%8C-%E7%96%91%E5%9B%A0%E5%8F%B0%E5%89%8D%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E8%BE%AD%E6%BC%94</a>"},{"pid":"6f29f342122e7cb2d1f47fd322bac78a3893e9fb","tid":1727640,"uid":327414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:45:00.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187a4e3d4e0